title: 'Disable the pppd_for_user SELinux Boolean'

description: |-
    By default, the SELinux boolean <tt>pppd_for_user</tt> is disabled.
    If this setting is enabled, it should be disabled.
    <sebool-macro enable="false" sebool="pppd_for_user" />

